description: Updates the Amazon QuickSight settings in your Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID for the Amazon Web Services account that contains the Amazon QuickSight settings that you want to list.

parameters.name: DefaultNamespace
parameters.description: The default namespace for this Amazon Web Services account. Currently, the default is default. IAM users that register for the first time with Amazon QuickSight provide an email address that becomes associated with the default namespace.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
